Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-[birds chirping]\N-[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Hilda ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman vocalizing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You're not a crazy rumor after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're real!\N-And also hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Last to join, first to get eaten.\N-What? Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[hound growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Frida!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, all he wants\Nis something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-No kidding.\N-So let's feed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Frida] Feed him what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please don't say us.\N-These!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on!\N-[David whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-[flashlight clicks]\N-[Raven Leader] Hilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,David!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's that? Frida?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's-- It's the Black Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He-- He's here and he's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-He tried to eat us.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's eating my snacks instead,\Nso everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[distant roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get everyone\Nout of here, immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[siren blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, Sparrow Scouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,due to an unexpected,\Num, wildlife situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we are breaking camp early,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but we will do so\Nin a calm, orderly fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[distant roar, howling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, no! We're all gonna be eaten!\N-The Black Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, you should be packing,\Nnot panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[David grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-[sighs] Here, let me help you.\N-I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-You were right, you know.\N-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,About my new so-called, huh, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[David grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness sake,\Nwill you just let me help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the end... like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I wish I could have spoken up\Nto those marra the way you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that felt pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,until we almost got eaten\Nby a giant hound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I've been acting like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish packing this, please?\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to find Tontu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave him out there\Nwith the Black Hound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He could get eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so out of the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, who's Tontu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Raven Leader] Hilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You will stay here and pack up\Nyour gear this instant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or you will not be allowed\Nto come on future camping trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[kids chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] Mum's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents don't know I'm out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh, could you give me a lift?\N-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm just so relieved\Nthat everybody's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure they'll catch\Nthat thing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A creature that big\Nshouldn't be too hard to find, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're disappointed\Nabout not getting the camping badge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've earned plenty\Nof other badges this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[sheepish laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you doing?\N-Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Frida, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] This is Tontu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a nisse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and he was thrown out\Nof his house by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure he didn't do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sure. Trust me. He--\N-Hilda... I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, does that mean\Nyou'll help me look for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-See you tomorrow?\N-See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to follow up on what your mum said\Nabout your badges,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,do you even have a single badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have\Nthe perfect plan to get you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I want you to earn\Nthe Fund Raising badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe I should go along.\NThat thing is still out there, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are safety patrols\Nin every neighborhood now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-And he's only been seen at night.\N-Even my parents are okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See? We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] All right,\Nbut stay together at all times
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and stick to the busy streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You may end up with even more badges\Nthan I earned my first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. [sheepish laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Sparrow Scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[David] Hello, we're collecting\Nfor Sparrow Scouts' jumble sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tontu said he used to live\Nin a yellow house with a duck pond
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,before he was kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Hilda] Hey, who are those guys?\N-[Frida sighs] Safety patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're searching for the hound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they going to do to it\Nwhen they find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, why are you dressed\Nlike a Sparrow Scout?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am a Sparrow Scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good! I've got a donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! People are being really generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not my Fluff-bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, ahem...  I don't care. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never a good idea\Nto throw away your real friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Tontu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[echoing] Tontu, are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-[cat screeching]\N-[Twig growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Twig grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Twig?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-[grunts]\N-Tontu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tontu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, just make sure you meet us\Nat the Sparrow Scout Hall by 3:00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or else you won't get credit\Nfor the badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tontu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, that's me.\N-No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, I'm looking for a different Tontu.\N-But we're all called "Tontu."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] That's confusing,\Nbut good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're out here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisse are being banished all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why you're all being banished?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse 1] We don't talk to each other,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse 2] No, nisses don't enjoy\Neach other's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I've seen that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse 3] I was kicked out,\Nand it wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse 4] My house-man\Nthrew me out for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse 5] I was framed.\NI didn't trash that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of other nisses\Nare saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse 5] I'm sure\Nthe rest of them are lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not totally sure how this works,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but isn't there a lot of unused\Nor hidden space outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you make a cozy nest there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse 5] The place of which you speak\Nis vast and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows where one would emerge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The nisse who ventures there\Nis likely never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the guy you're looking for\Nwent back to the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so bothered anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no worse off than when you met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'm supposed to be\Nat the Scout Hall right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twig!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting] Sorry I'm a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Raven Leader just left.\NWe stalled for as long as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least you found Tontu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[news anchor] {\i1}News just in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trolberg city officials say{\i0}\N{\i1}they have reason to believe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that three people{\i0}\N{\i1}have been eaten by the hound.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Details to--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to hear that before bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's focus on something positive,\Nlike the badge ceremony tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd make a great Sparrow Scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it just runs in the family, right?\N[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really very proud of you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mum is going to be so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And today I blew my last chance at a badge\Nbecause I was busy looking for Tontu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fix that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You both need to sign\Na Disappointment Deferral Agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can add in additional clauses\Nthat address hidden resentments
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,or blaming tendencies.\NIt's very simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alfur, humans just don't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus we arrive at my own feelings\Nof disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-[distant howling]\N-[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are, all cozy, and poor Tontu\Nis out there in the rain with that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is that thing\Nis actually a barghest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a barghest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A kind of wild, giant dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, what it's doing in Trolberg\Nis a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Barghests usually live\Ndeep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then he's lost\Nand probably scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[hound howling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And definitely hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure it's okay to get a ride\Nwith David and Frida?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go straight to Scout Hall\Nafter my client meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See you at the badge ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens, closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think I'll walk\Nto the ceremony and look for Tontu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the day won't be a total loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[bus hisses]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[duck quacking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[quacking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yellow duck, yellow house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I already gave my donation\Nto some Sparrow Scouts just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just passing, and I was wondering\Ndid a nisse ever live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, dear.\NNot anymore, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind if I asked what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I caught him stealing, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could possibly\Nhave been mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the most dreadful racket,\Nlike someone was smashing up my kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came down to see what was going on,{\i0}\N{\i1}and there he was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'd ransacked the whole place{\i0}\N{\i1}looking for something to steal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must have gotten bored with{\i0}\N{\i1}all the things he'd swiped over the years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because that was everywhere, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said I had\Nso much junk for your jumble sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, donations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your time, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-[clattering]\N-[voice murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Hilda] Tontu!\N-[Tontu] Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're fine.\NI've been so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] Can't believe your mum\Nlet you go out on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with that monster on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a monster. It's a barghest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mum thinks I'm getting a lift\Nto the ceremony with David and Frida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to tell her\Nthat I'm not getting any badges
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because of you, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why lie about something like that?\N-Why lie about why you were kicked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That nice lady said you trashed her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] She's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely innocent. Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're capable of it.\NEvery nisse says the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're all probably lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course\Nthat's what they'd say about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I've spent so much time\Nlooking for you and worrying about you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because I felt I ought to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I don't know if I should've bothered,\Nand you're not even grateful that I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] What? This is\Nwhat I look like when I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, why don't you check\Nthis place out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Scout Hall must have\Nloads of Nowhere Space, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not good,\Njust meet me afterwards, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Up next: Frida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have achieved your level three\NHelpful and Friendly badge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,along with your Fund Raising, First Aid,\NStonework, and Young Entrepreneur badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can all agree\Nthat's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Raven Leader]\NNext: David for his Fund Raising...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-[hound growling]\N-...and Cycling badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu gasps] Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and also his Friend to Insects badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-[cricket chirping]\N-There's a bug on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that concludes\Nthis year's badge ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[applause]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Tontu] Hilda!\N-[kids gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[crowd gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tontu?\N-[Tontu] We've gotta go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[crowd gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all screaming]\N-[boy] It's the Black Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all shouting]\N-[Raven Leader] Please keep calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep calm, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Tontu] Oh...\N-[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] Come on! [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] Jump! Through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Tontu grunts]\N-[cat yowling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Frida's lost book?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu shouts, panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is Frida's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-In here! [groans]\N-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[pants] This is my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would ask you kindly to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Jellybean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Jellybean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[both] Jellybean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my dog Jellybean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him since he was a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I found him a long time ago{\i0}\N{\i1}when I was little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did what nisses do with lost things{\i0}\N{\i1}and took him home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I looked after him in secret for a while,{\i0}\N{\i1}but when my parents found him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they took him off me{\i0}\N{\i1}and I never saw him again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never understood why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have known\Nwhat he'd grow up to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew he would get so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] But is he dangerous?\NHe ate people, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Three at last count.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[whispering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[gagging]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[all screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess he sort of ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda? Hilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[sniffing]\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Mum. This is Jellybean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-This explains everything.\N-[Tontu] Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taught how to use the nisse spaces\Nwhen he was a puppy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so of course he's been using them\Nto hide and move around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time he goes through a nisse's nest,\Nhe's so massive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he takes everything with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then he trashes whatever room{\i0}\N{\i1}he happens to arrive in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all happens so fast that he's gone{\i0}\N{\i1}before you know what's going on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're all getting kicked out.\NHe's been framing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that's what happened to me?\NWouldn't I have seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] It's a wonder you can see\Nanything at all with that haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[police siren wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[sirens blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Those are the men looking for the hound.\N-You have to get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, maybe it's best if we just--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you think,\Nbut he's really a very dangerous animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a puppy.\NHe's no different from Twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hilda...\N-[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I don't have a badge to prove it,\Nbut I am still a friend to animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't hurt anyone\Nand I won't let anyone hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-[siren chirping]\N-[hound whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's panicking.\N-[nisse] How far are the city walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could get him outside,\Nmaybe they'd let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires squealing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jellybean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, seat belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[nisse] Jellybean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mum] Oh, I can see the town gate.\NWe're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] What happens\Nif he catches up with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all shout]\N-[Mum] Oh, the brakes aren't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tontu, quick, take my hand.\N-[Tontu] Whoa, whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're thinking.\NIt's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tontu, we're going to crash!\N-[Tontu] Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] That place\Nis the place we never go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for dragging you through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And we escaped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-But... where are the others?\N-We got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be\Nthousands of miles away right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,if they even made it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I've got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found my sewing kit,\Nso I thought I'd make an addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm sorry that I pressured you\Nabout getting badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that you're the kindest,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,bravest, most selfless girl\Nit is possible to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hot chocolates are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No marshmallows for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Loads of marshmallows for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This report will set off\Na golden age of elf exploration!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Just think\Nof all the missing paperwork
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that may have fallen into Nowhere Space!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably David and Frida.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Tontu] I'll get more hot chocolate.\N[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get some biscuits and Dragon Panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a kind of a badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please find a reason\Nfor this not to be on my arm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,before the next Sparrow Scout meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Maybe Tontu could, you know, "borrow it"?\N-[Tontu] Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Frida] I know!\NTwig could snag it with an antler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur]\NOr we could pay a visit to the lindworm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and have it lightly scorched.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[woffs calling]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[elves murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man whistling tune]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] This was once\Na cozy little house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who lived here\Nbefriended a giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-I guess she learned her lesson.\N-Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Odds are... she'd do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[folk music playing]
